metadata.title: Protracted Offshore Sections (Base 5)

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Alaska Department of Natural Resources, Division of Support Services-Land Records Information Section

metadata.description: Data Type: Base Maps  ;Section boundaries were generated using BLM and DNR computer programs for the construction of digital aliquot parts. The programs make calculations from the radian measurements representing township corner coordinates. This coverage is intended to geographically represent DNR's protracted sections for offshore townships and is not capable of supporting survey quality area calculations.
